en der alten Wissenschaft, d.h. des Ayurveda, f\u00fcr die Behandlung der Gichtarthritis zu nutzen.\nAutorenportrait\nLaurea in Ayurveda nel 2003 e post-laurea in kayachikitsa (medicina) nel 2008 presso lo State Ayurvedic College and Hospital, Lucknow University Lucknow Uttar Pradesh India. Ora lavora come docente presso lo State Ayurvedic College and Hospital, Lucknow University Lucknow Uttar Pradesh India dal 2013.", "language": null, "image": "https://herrholgersson.de/profiles/bhwp/modules/bhwp/webshopgatherer/img/no_image.png", "pagetype": "book", "links": ["#main-content", "/", "/cart", "/cart", "/account", "/", "/shop", "/shop/ebooks", "/buchtipps", "/bildergalerie/have-look-inside", "/veranstaltungstermine", "/herr-holgerssons-news", "/herr-holgersson-liest-im-kreis", "/", "/shop", "/shop/item/9786205000120", "/shop/search?autor=Garg%2C%20Richa", "/shop/search?verlag=Verlag%20Unser%20Wissen", "/shop/search?wg=696", "/lieferung-und-zahlung", "/cart/add/nojs/9786205000120", "/account/wishes/add/nojs/9786205000120", "https://herrholgersson.de/shop/item/9789811978791/industry-4-0-and-the-digital-transformation-of-international-business-von-gurinder-singh-richa-goel-vikas-garg-gebundenes-buch", "https://herrholgersson.de/shop/item/9789811978791/industry-4-0-and-the-digital-transformation-of-international-business-von-gurinder-singh-richa-goel-vikas-garg-gebundenes-buch", "/shop/search?autor=Gurinder%20Singh/Richa%20Goel/Vikas%20Garg", "/shop/search?verlag=Springer%20Verlag%20GmbH", "/cart/add/nojs/9789811978791", "/lieferung-und-zahlung", "https://herrholgersson.de/shop/item/9786200310866/a-concept-of-vatashonita-in-ayurveda-w-s-r-to-gouty-arthritis-von-richa-garg-kartoniertes-buch", "https://herrholgersson.de/shop/item/9786200310866/a-concept-of-vatashonita-in-ayurveda-w-s-r-to-gouty-arthritis-von-richa-garg-kartoniertes-buch", "/shop/search?autor=Garg%2C%20Richa", "/shop/search?verlag=LAP%20Lambert%20Academic%20Publishing", "/cart/add/nojs/9786200310866", "/lie